{"word":"βράχεα","slug":"βράχεα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βράχεα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>as if from a <a href='S:nominative'>nom.</a> <el>βράχος</el>, or <el>βραχέα</el> (<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> of <a href='S:βραχύς'><el>βραχύς</el></a>)\n<p/><i>shallows</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>brevia</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}